すべてのクラス

クラス 説明
AbstractHistory
Abstract class for aggregating versions (StructureEntityVersion) of a source code entity (i.e. a class, a method or an attribute).
AbstractRefactoringHelper
Refactoring helpers support Distiller in deciding whether an added and a deleted class/field/method represent a refactoring.
ASTHelper<T extends StructureNode>
Handles language specific ASTs and provides access to their content.
ASTHelperFactory
Factory interface to create ASTHelper from a File and a version number.
ASTNodeTypeConverter
AST node type converters should extend this class to facilitate conversion of AST node types.
AttributeHistory
Attribute histories store change data about the history of an attribute.
BestLeafTreeMatcher
Implementation of the best matching tree matcher.
ChangeDistiller
Factory for creating the FileDistiller for a particular ChangeDistiller.Language.
ChangeDistiller.Language
Programming languages that ChangeDistiller can handle.
ChangeModifier
Modifier representation used by ChangeDistiller.
ChangeType
All change types that are extracted by ChangeDistiller and stored as SourceCodeChange.
ChawatheCalculator
Implementation of the default inner node similarity calculator proposed by Chawathe.
ClassDistiller
Extracts changes from a class StructureDiffNode.
ClassHistory
Class histories store change data about the history of a class.
ClassRefactoringHelper
Helps finding refactorings of classes.
Comment
AST node representing any kind of comment.
Comment.CommentType
Type of comments that java provides.
CommentCleaner
Removes dead code comments and joins successive line comments.
CommentCollector
Collects comments for a CompilationUnitDeclaration.
CommentRecorderParser
Internal parser used for parsing source to create DOM AST nodes.
Delete
Source code change that represents the delete of an entity.
DeleteOperation
Representation of the delete basic TreeEditOperation.
Distiller
Distills and classifies SourceCodeChange between two Node trees.
DistillerFactory
Factory interface to create Distiller working with a StructureEntityVersion.
EntityType
All types for source code entities that are used by ChangeDistiller to build up the AST (abstract syntax tree).
FieldRefactoringHelper
Helps finding refactorings of fields.
FileDistiller
Distills SourceCodeChanges between two File.
FileUtils
Utility class to handle Files.
Insert
Source code change that represents the insert of an entity.
InsertOperation
Representation of the insert basic TreeEditOperation.
InvalidSyntaxException
Thrown if a file has syntax errors.
JavaASTHelper
Implementation of ASTHelper for the Java programming language.
JavaASTNodeTypeConverter
Implementation of ASTNodeTypeConverter for the Java programming language.
JavaChangeDistillerModule
Injection module to configure ChangeDistiller with the Java programming language.
JavaCompilation
Container for CompilationUnitDeclaration and the corresponding Scanner.
JavaCompilationUtils
Utility class for Java compilation.
JavaDeclarationConverter
Visitor to generate an intermediate tree (general, rooted, labeled, valued tree) out of a field, class, or method declaration.
JavaEntityType
Implementation of EntityType for the Java language.
JavaMethodBodyConverter
Visitor to generate an intermediate tree (general, rooted, labeled, valued tree) out of a method body.
JavaSourceCodeChangeClassifier
Implementation of SourceCodeChangeClassifier for the Java language.
JavaStructureNode
Node for Java structure differencing.
JavaStructureNode.Type
Java structure node types.
JavaStructureTreeBuilder
Creates a tree of JavaStructureNodes.
LeafPair
Pair of leafs
LevenshteinSimilarityCalculator
Implementation of a StringSimilarityCalculator based on the Levenshtein distance.
MatchingFactory
Factory to generate a TreeMatcher out of specified preference values.
MethodHistory
Method histories store change data about the history of an method.
MethodRefactoringHelper
Helps finding refactorings of methods.
Move
Source code change that represents the move of an entity.
MoveOperation
Representation of the move basic TreeEditOperation.
NGramsCalculator
Implementation of the ngrams similarity measure.
Node
General tree node.
NodePair
A pair of nodes.
NodeSimilarityCalculator
Interface for (inner) node similarity calculators.
RefactoringCandidate
A refactoring candidate is a container class that stores a SourceCodeChange with a StructureDiffNode.
RefactoringCandidateContainer
Container for RefactoringCandidates.
RefactoringCandidateProcessor
Processes RefactoringCandidates from a RefactoringCandidateContainer and adds resulting changes to the ClassHistory, and its member histories respectively.
RefactoringExtractor
Provides a method to extract refactorings from a list of added and a list of deleted entities.
RefactoringPair
A refacotring pair is a container for storing to RefactoringCandidates.
SignificanceLevel
Significance level of an extracted SourceCodeChange.
SourceCodeChange
General (abstract) representation of a source code change.
SourceCodeChangeClassifier
Classifies SourceCodeChanges into ChangeTypes
SourceCodeChangeConverter
Converts TreeEditOperations to SourceCodeChanges and attaches them to a StructureEntityVersion in which the changes happened.
SourceCodeChangeFactory
Factory for SourceCodeChange creation out of TreeEditOperation.
SourceCodeEntity
Source code entity representing one particular AST node.
SourceRange
Representation of a range in a document with start and end.
StringSimilarityCalculator
Interface for string similarity calculators.
StructureDifferencer
Calculates structure differences between two trees of StructureNodes.
StructureDifferencer.DiffType
Types of differences.
StructureDiffNode
Node container for structure differences.
StructureEntityVersion
A structure entity version consists of all SourceCodeChanges applied in a version of an attribute, a class, or a method.
StructureNode
Node for structure differencing.
TokenBasedCalculator
Implementation of a token based string similarity calculator.
TreeDifferencer
Implementation of the core tree differencing algorithm of Chawathe.
TreeEditOperation
Interface for basic tree edit operations.
TreeEditOperation.OperationType
Type of TreeEditOperation.
TreeMatcher
Interface for all tree matcher.
Update
Source code change that represents the update of an entity.
UpdateOperation
Representation of the update basic TreeEditOperation.
